lead_paragraph: Feyenoord have reached an agreement in principle with Brad Jones to sign the former Liverpool goalkeeper on a one-year contract pending a medical, the Dutch club said in a statement.

headline.print_headline: Feyenoord Reach Agreement to Sign Goalkeeper Jones
